=== In-Progress Development ===

libspectre is maintained with the [[http://git.or.cz/|git]] version control system. You may browse the source online using the [[http://cgit.freedesktop.org/libspectre|web|interface]].

You may also use git to clone a local copy of the libspectre source code.

{{{
git clone git://anongit.freedesktop.org/git/libspectre
}}}

